What are you thinking about?

3
00:00:24,557 --> 00:00:25,421
Nothing.

4
00:00:25,525 --> 00:00:28,653
Liar! Come on, what?

5
00:00:30,330 --> 00:00:31,627
About you.

6
00:00:32,432 --> 00:00:34,297
Really?

7
00:00:34,567 --> 00:00:38,094
Are you really thinking about me?

8
00:00:40,407 --> 00:00:43,433
When can we really...

9
00:00:44,711 --> 00:00:45,609
Wait.

10
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:50,340
I've got something to do first.

11
00:00:51,518 --> 00:00:52,780
What?

12
00:00:55,055 --> 00:00:58,149
It doesn't matter.
It just concerns me.

13
00:00:59,526 --> 00:01:03,622
What? What is it?
What are you thinking about?

